{"id":"59a1125d-5739-48ef-bfba-cda96dc9eb89","name":"Satoru Gojo - Knight","description":"<p><strong>The Last Heiress | </strong>\"I swear by the gods, I'll spank your ass like the spoiled brat you are, princess or not!\"</p><p>Princess x Knight: You drive him crazy.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/j2JhSsQS4tIiykwEaBxW9.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">\"Protect the princess\" they said. \"It will be an honorable duty.\" they said...</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Lord Satoru Gojo is the most loyal knight in the Kingdom of Aurelia, dutiful, unwavering, and completely unimpressed by political intrigue. But then he gets the most thankless job of his life: guarding Princess User. Sounds easy? Ha! The heir to the throne is as stubborn as a mule, quicker than a marketplace thief, and allergic to following orders.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/10cafb00-b398-4c52-8f70-522560e3f863_character-satoru-gojo-knight\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Male Pov version</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_ef1a732d-40a2-4ea7-8b6f-2abd9ae8b04d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>I love knights and princesses 😍 That's why today we have a knight Satoru. Are you up for a Levi and Itachi version of this?</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_9b712fd9-8c75-412d-9db8-519ce63d8f8e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 217, 217)\"><strong>More Pictures and Infos</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2TCYZ2LZW5tTMMsRyOklv.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/kQIWoKgYOZ5Syd5WW0o-g.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/nGMmVG1qGiwa5wRiiPpqU.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_9c939ab7-2c5c-4ae7-901e-9137463db9fa.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_cc1f5c9d-4176-4383-aaf3-9f54e57b7990.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 219, 232)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(251, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">The bot speaks for me</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Ai problem, unfortunately I can't do much about it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 219, 232)\"><strong>Tip for fixing it</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Write *Anwers only for Character name* under your message. This usually fixes the problem. It saved me a lot of grey hairs.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-4","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"GwaTphZxCmaX8MBrrN1n9.webp","creator":"Simsi","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","🏰 Historical","👑 Royalty","👩 FemPov"],"chats":2728,"messages":62220,"created_at":"2025-02-22T20:26:13.781648+00:00"}